        </table>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">6. International Transfers</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
        All data processing occurs within the European Union. We do not transfer data outside the EU/EEA.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
        Since we don't collect or store personal data, there is no personal data to access, rectify, or delete. If you have concerns, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@runlater.eu" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300">support@runlater.eu</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
